Main ..> LoginFrame
LoginFrame ..> LoginService
LoginFrame ..> MainAppFrame
MainAppFrame ..> RoleAccessService
MainAppFrame ..> DashboardPanel
MainAppFrame ..> EmployeePanel
MainAppFrame ..> TeamOperationsPanel
MainAppFrame ..> HRPanel
MainAppFrame ..> PayrollPanel
